text: Győr (; , ) is the sixth-largest city in Hungary and the capital of Győr- Moson-Sopron county. In 2016, 131.267 people lived there. ==Twin towns − Sister cities== Győr is twinned with: * Kuopio, Finland * Erfurt, Germany * Sindelfingen, Germany * Ingolstadt, Germany * Colmar, France * Bryansk, Russia * Brașov, Romania * Nazareth Illit, Israel * Wuhan, China * Poznań, Poland * Montevideo, Uruguay ==Other websites== * Official site Category:Cities in Hungary Category:Győr-Moson-Sopron County
title: Győr
